    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is a rare find! We are excited to present this stunning vehicle that is in absolute mint condition. It looks and drives as if it just came off the assembly line, featuring a flawless exterior and a pristine interior. If you're looking for perfection and a vehicle that has been meticulously cared for, this is the one for you!",
